---

## 🎨 Design Principles

1. **Code Ownership** - Users own 100% of component code
2. **Zero Runtime Deps** - No proprietary runtime dependencies
3. **Framework Support** - React, Next.js, Vue, Nuxt with equal quality
4. **World-Class Design** - UI quality matching top design agencies
5. **Accessibility First** - WCAG 2.1 AA compliance minimum
6. **Performance Obsessed** - Minimal bundle impact
7. **Premium Aesthetics** - Every component should WOW users
8. **Fully Customizable** - Easy to modify and extend
9. **Pixel Perfect** - Attention to micro-details

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

### Core
- **TypeScript** 5.0+
- **Tailwind CSS** 3.4+
- **Framer Motion** (React animations)
- **Motion One** (Vue animations)
- **Lucide Icons**

### Build Tools
- **Vite** - Development and build
- **pnpm** - Monorepo management
- **Vitest** - Unit testing
- **Playwright** - E2E testing
- **VitePress/Astro** - Documentation

### Architecture
- Monorepo structure
- CLI tool for component installation
- Framework-specific adapters
- Shared core utilities

---

## 📅 Development Roadmap

### Phase 1: Foundation (Months 1-3)
**Goal:** Core infrastructure and essential components

**Deliverables:**
- ✅ 15 foundation components (React + Vue)
- ✅ CLI tool with framework detection
- ✅ Premium design system
- ✅ Documentation site (shadcn/ui style)
- ✅ Testing infrastructure
- ✅ v0.1.0 release

**Target:** 1K GitHub stars, 5K monthly downloads

---

### Phase 2: Expansion (Months 4-6)
**Goal:** Advanced components and glassmorphic UI

**Deliverables:**
- ✅ 20 additional components (overlay, feedback, navigation)
- ✅ 8 glassmorphic components
- ✅ Next.js and Nuxt optimizations
- ✅ Interactive playground
- ✅ Accessibility audit (WCAG 2.1 AA)
- ✅ v1.0.0 stable release

**Target:** 5K GitHub stars, 15K monthly downloads

---

### Phase 3: Premium Features (Months 7-9)
**Goal:** Differentiating animated components

**Deliverables:**
- ✅ 12 premium animated components
- ✅ Advanced theming system
- ✅ Figma design kit
- ✅ Video tutorials
- ✅ Community showcase
- ✅ v1.5.0 release

**Target:** 15K GitHub stars, 30K monthly downloads

---

### Phase 4: Ecosystem (Months 10-12)
**Goal:** Complete ecosystem

**Deliverables:**
- ✅ Form builder
- ✅ Dashboard templates
- ✅ E-commerce templates
- ✅ VSCode extension
- ✅ Advanced data components
- ✅ v2.0.0 major release

**Target:** 25K GitHub stars, 75K monthly downloads

---

## 📖 Documentation Structure

### Layout (shadcn/ui Inspired)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Header (Logo, Search, GitHub, Theme)      │
├──────────┬──────────────────┬──────────────┤
│  Left    │  Main Content    │  Right       │
│  Sidebar │                  │  "On This    │
│          │  - Installation  │   Page"      │
│  - Intro │  - Usage         │              │
│  - Comp. │  - API Ref       │  - Links     │
│    - Base│  - Examples      │  - Headings  │
│    - Form│  - Variants      │  - Scroll    │
│    - Data│  - Live Preview  │              │
│    - Feed│                  │  [Sticky]    │
│    - Over│  [Scrollable]    │              │
│    - Nav │                  │              │
│    - Glass                  │              │
│    - Anim│                  │              │
└──────────┴──────────────────┴──────────────┘
```

### Features
- **Left Sidebar:** Component navigation with active highlighting
- **Main Content:** Live previews, code examples, API docs
- **Right Sidebar:** "On This Page" TOC with auto-scroll
- **Framework Switcher:** Toggle React/Vue/Next/Nuxt examples
- **Dark Mode:** Toggle for all previews
- **Copy Buttons:** One-click code copying

